806
01:16:29,505 --> 01:16:30,421
Kabede.

807
01:16:33,088 --> 01:16:34,005
Ah, claro.

808
01:16:39,588 --> 01:16:41,005
O que a CIA está fazendo aqui?

809
01:16:42,046 --> 01:16:43,588
